Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.85,0:01:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Halo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.24,0:01:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat datang di Elf Garden!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.27,0:01:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.03,0:01:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Reservasi atas nama Tonome.\N- Wanginya!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.23,0:01:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami sudah menunggumu\Nuntuk pengalaman teh racikan asli.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.46,0:01:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari kuantar ke meja.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.97,0:02:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pilih daun teh dengan mempertimbangkan\Nhasil akhirnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.30,0:02:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tonome, kau suka teh apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.42,0:02:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pilih teh berdasarkan efeknya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.50,0:02:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untuk konsentrasi atau relaksasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.01,0:02:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana denganmu, Yako?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.38,0:02:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Coba kupikir...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.67,0:02:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, teh seduhanmu kemarin, aku suka itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.56,0:02:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau terlalu baik...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.62,0:02:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh! Aku yang meracik teh itu untuknya!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.85,0:02:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.36,0:02:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pacarmu datang ke toko kami\Nbeberapa hari lalu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.52,0:02:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Katanya ingin membuat pacarnya senang.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.46,0:02:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pacar yang luar biasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.18,0:02:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, bagaimana rasanya kencan\Ndengan pria tak kasatmata?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.25,0:02:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah lama pacaran?\NSiap menikah? Tinggal bersama?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.51,0:02:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, kami belum sampai tahap itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.70,0:02:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, "belum sampai"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.17,0:02:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, akan segera terjadi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.08,0:02:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, apa kalian akan melakukannya malam ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.52,0:02:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aduh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.38,0:03:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku!\NPemilik kami bodoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.16,0:03:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah! Aku dihukum elf putih!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.74,0:03:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Diam, Elf Gelap!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.78,0:03:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.43,0:03:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf. Pasti canggung bagimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.16,0:03:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anu...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.31,0:03:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mumpung di sini, aku akan senang\Njika kau meracik teh untukku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.91,0:03:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.07,0:03:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akan kuracik teh khusus untukmu, Tonome.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.56,0:03:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku menantikannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.18,0:03:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, nantikan saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.98,0:03:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagus! Itu semua berkat aku!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.41,0:03:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan melunjak.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.89,0:03:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.86,0:03:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Izinkan aku siapkan teh\Ndengan daun pilihan kalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.33,0:03:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meracik teh sangat menyenangkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.14,0:03:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, aku tak sabar meminumnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.75,0:03:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Anu...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.88,0:03:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kau cari info toko ini khusus untukku?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.62,0:03:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Teh tempo hari untuk memutuskan\Napa kita harus pergi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.61,0:04:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.60,0:04:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, tidak, lupakan!\NAku bisa sangat egois! Maaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.85,0:04:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya aku ketahuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.56,0:04:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Ah! Maafkan aku!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.98,0:04:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku cenderung menebak motif orang...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.01,0:04:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mata batinmu melihat segalanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.02,0:04:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bisa jadi asisten detektif hebat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.89,0:04:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ti-Tidak sama sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.87,0:04:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Banyak hal yang tidak kutahu,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.14,0:04:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}termasuk dirimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.99,0:04:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak bisa bayangkan\Npenampilanmu tanpa menyentuhmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.29,0:04:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau mau menyentuhku?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.02,0:04:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.67,0:04:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tanganku, mungkin?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.70,0:04:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.46,0:04:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Silakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.42,0:04:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, jarimu lebih kurus daripada ayahku.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.54,0:04:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kukumu dipotong rapi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.06,0:04:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski tak terlihat, itu perawatan penting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.84,0:04:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku lega. Aku tak bisa melihatnya,\Njadi penasaran apakah hasilnya baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.35,0:05:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku paham perasaan itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.74,0:05:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga tak bisa lihat kukuku,\Ntapi aku tak mau terlihat tak pantas!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.60,0:05:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar. Yako,\Nkukumu juga dipotong rapi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.24,0:05:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah! Rasanya dia bisa melihat menembusku!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.62,0:05:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf menunggu lama.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.49,0:05:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini teh pilihan kalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.14,0:05:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Harum sekali. Mari kita cicipi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.99,0:05:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.18,0:05:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jarashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.01,0:05:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.18,0:05:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana biasanya Tonome berpakaian?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.42,0:05:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.68,0:05:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana dia berpakaian?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.18,0:05:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biasanya dia pakai setelan jas.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.66,0:05:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelan macam apa?\NMaksudnya, gaya apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.30,0:05:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.94,0:05:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm... Gaya pria Inggris?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.30,0:05:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pria Inggris? Keren sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.97,0:05:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar! Pria Inggris adalah mata-mata hebat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.15,0:05:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.24,0:06:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pria Inggris itu mata-mata?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.45,0:06:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hanya di film.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.39,0:06:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.53,0:06:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}setelan Tonome adalah setelan bisnis.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.04,0:06:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untuk apa kau cari tahu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.76,0:06:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eng... Aku mau beli pakaian,\Njadi butuh informasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.51,0:06:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.04,0:06:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa perlu tahu tentang Tonome\Njika kau yang beli pakaian?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.97,0:06:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan bilang...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.59,0:06:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kau ingin pakai baju kembaran?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.03,0:06:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.39,0:06:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah? Tidak juga...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.89,0:06:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jelas itu yang akan dia kenakan\Nsaat kencan, Kucing Bodoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.10,0:06:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sebut aku apa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.70,0:06:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aduh! Aduh! Aduh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.01,0:06:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, itu untuk... kencan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.23,0:06:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan Tonome?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.08,0:06:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu... Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.69,0:06:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu, Shizuka!\NKau harus pakai pakaian terbaikmu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.65,0:06:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pakaian terbaik itu berlebihan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.69,0:06:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah! Tolong rahasiakan ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.62,0:06:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hanya ada kita berempat di agensi, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.60,0:06:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku selalu beli pakaian jenis yang sama\Nagar tidak salah pilih.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.60,0:07:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi sekarang... aku ingin pakai sesuatu\Nuntuk hari istimewa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.33,0:07:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shizuka! Serahkan padaku!\NAku akan menemanimu belanja!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.55,0:07:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.20,0:07:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Te-Terima kasih!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.09,0:07:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Jarashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.14,0:07:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.11,0:07:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bisa jadi tidak pengertian dan egois,\Njadi fokuslah pada kebutuhan Yako.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.89,0:07:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau juga pemarah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.02,0:07:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.98,0:07:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau buktikan ucapanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.45,0:07:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.06,0:07:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagus sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.91,0:07:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Manisnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.72,0:07:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Apa menurutmu begitu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.73,0:07:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pakaianmu biasanya feminin dan agak kasual.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.34,0:07:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Punya pakaian elegan dan dewasa\Nakan sangat berguna.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.42,0:07:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Coba yang ini juga!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.40,0:07:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, tu-tunggu sebentar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.42,0:07:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.99,0:07:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin memeriksa seperti apa pakaian ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.49,0:07:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Analisis selesai. Kain biru muda.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.90,0:07:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm... Biru muda...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.34,0:07:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.87,0:07:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shizuka, akan kujelaskan padamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.60,0:07:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah? Terima kasih banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.08,0:07:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.19,0:08:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kainnya punya tampilan sangat penuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.70,0:08:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seperti apa rasanya tampilan penuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.55,0:08:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Polanya seperti lipatan kertas,\Njadi tampak penuh, mungkin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.98,0:08:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benarkah?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.14,0:08:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.05,0:08:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf. Aku benar-benar tidak pengertian.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.41,0:08:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.39,0:08:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau memikirkan ucapan Kikira?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.80,0:08:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ti-Tidak, tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.06,0:08:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tempo hari, aku salah parkir sepeda\Ndan hampir membuatmu tersandung.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sikapmu tak seperti biasanya, Jarashi.\NKau makan sesuatu yang aneh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.75,0:08:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan makan apa pun di lantai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.38,0:08:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.69,0:08:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.38,0:08:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh? Jadi, kau juga tahu\Ncara memancing emosi, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.57,0:08:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.83,0:08:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah! Karena sudah selesai belanja,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.86,0:08:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku akan membawamu ke tempat langgananku!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.32,0:08:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.58,0:08:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo ke sana!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.99,0:08:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, Kikira,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.13,0:08:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}apakah ada restoran rekomendasi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.26,0:09:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayolah, coba lanjutkan pembicaraan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.53,0:09:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terlalu merepotkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.13,0:09:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, begitu.\NAku berharap dapat rekomendasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.31,0:09:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah, kembali bekerja.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.09,0:09:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menyeringai.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.84,0:09:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak perlu diberi tahu\Nsoal ekspresimu! Pergi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.36,0:09:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Silakan masuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.84,0:09:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, hei!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.67,0:09:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian pelanggan tempo hari!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.42,0:09:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian dari toko teh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.98,0:09:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, benar!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.05,0:09:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku Karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.42,0:09:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Istrinya, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.82,0:09:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami pasangan elf!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.35,0:09:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu meresahkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.97,0:09:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang mencurigakan berkerudung putih...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.63,0:09:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka parkir di seberang jalan toko.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.42,0:10:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka tanya warga sekitar tentang kami,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.15,0:10:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan memotret kami dari mobil.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.23,0:10:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu mengkhawatirkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.34,0:10:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.40,0:10:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selama 100 tahun,\Naku belum pernah punya penguntit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.05,0:10:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sangat bersemangat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.28,0:10:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, tapi kau gelisah, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.16,0:10:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya mereka juga mengikuti kami\Nke mana-mana.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.56,0:10:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu, apa mereka mengikuti...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.82,0:10:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan khawatir!\NKami lolos sebelum ke sini!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.04,0:10:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka tak tahu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.38,0:10:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa sungguh tidak apa-apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.45,0:10:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mengerti.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.76,0:10:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami akan cari tahu siapa mereka\Ndan menanganinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.92,0:10:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.29,0:10:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.58,0:10:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Tonome.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.08,0:10:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.84,0:10:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suar pelacak yang dipasang Jarashi
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.72,0:10:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ada di perusahaan farmasi besar,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.35,0:10:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"White Pharmaceutical" di pegunungan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.31,0:10:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selain itu, orang-orang di dalam mobil\Nselalu berpakaian sama,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.49,0:10:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi bentuk tubuhnya berbeda.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.10,0:10:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.43,0:10:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin menjadi masalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.29,0:10:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.07,0:10:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}apa maksudmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.12,0:10:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kemungkinan besar\Nseluruh organisasi terlibat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.85,0:11:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita mungkin bukan melawan penguntit biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.38,0:11:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untuk saat ini,\Nberi tahu Jarashi untuk waspada...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.16,0:11:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tonome, ada masalah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.91,0:11:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beberapa mobil berhenti di depan toko
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.39,0:11:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan sekelompok pria keluar!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.25,0:11:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku baru saja keluar lewat pintu belakang\Nbersama suami istri itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.92,0:11:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Luar biasa, seperti di film!\NSeru sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.55,0:11:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kau tak merasakan keadaan mendesak?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.50,0:11:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mengerti.\NKami segera ke sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.58,0:11:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jumlah mereka banyak. Aku ikut.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.51,0:11:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan jaga kantor!\NKalian berhati-hatilah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.09,0:11:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yako, mohon bantuannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.06,0:11:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semoga semua ini\Nbisa diselesaikan dengan damai...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.91,0:11:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Silakan masuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mau berkonsultasi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.12,0:11:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, kami tak lagi terima\Njanji temu hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.62,0:11:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sendirian di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.04,0:11:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah? Ya, aku...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.04,0:12:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jauhi dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.29,0:12:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah? Tonome?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.21,0:12:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sadar mereka mungkin\Ntargetkan agensi juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.21,0:12:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, aku...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.92,0:12:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku adalah elf!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.59,0:12:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Elf putih, sama seperti putriku!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.30,0:12:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.41,0:12:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini presdir perusahaan farmasi, ayahku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.72,0:12:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sungguh minta maaf atas masalah ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.85,0:12:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.39,0:12:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau datang untuk melihat putrimu\Ndan suaminya yang kawin lari.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.36,0:12:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayah, kenapa harus datang dengan\Nseluruh klan dan menyamar?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.87,0:12:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka semua ingin melihatmu,\Ndan kami tak ingin kau tahu...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.57,0:12:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau kunjungi agensi detektif\Nbeberapa hari lalu,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.82,0:12:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jadi aku pikir mungkin ada salah paham.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.56,0:12:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, kalian masih mengikuti.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.38,0:12:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, kau pria yang kikuk, Ayah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.70,0:12:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.71,0:12:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Asal tahu saja,\Naku masih belum menerimamu, Elf Gelap.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.62,0:13:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, ayolah! Aku tak minta\Npenerimaanmu, Ayah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.70,0:13:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hentikan itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.72,0:13:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.59,0:13:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku senang masalahnya sudah selesai?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.77,0:13:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya mereka tidak beranggapan begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.64,0:13:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kerja bagus hari ini, semuanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.91,0:13:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menyenangkan sekali mengadakan\Npesta minum kecil bersama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.07,0:13:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jarang ada kesempatan seperti ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.03,0:13:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku lebih suka pulang begitu sifku selesai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.86,0:13:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Merusak suasana.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.45,0:13:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku yakin kau tak dapat banyak wanita.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.28,0:13:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, aku punya pasangan.\NAku tak butuh wanita lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.03,0:13:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm? Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.79,0:13:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak tahu itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.50,0:13:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini kali pertama aku dengar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.90,0:13:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.04,0:13:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan memberiku selamat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.54,0:13:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku jadi ingat. Aku sudah lama penasaran,\Ntapi kau tidak minum, Shizuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.22,0:13:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku minum, tapi takut pulang jika mabuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.12,0:13:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasanya berbahaya jika indraku tidak tajam.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.35,0:14:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.42,0:14:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu,\Nbagaimana kalau aku antar pulang?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.76,0:14:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bisa minum malam ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.91,0:14:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah? Kau yakin?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.32,0:14:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja! Ayo, mau minum apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.47,0:14:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, apakah ada minuman manis?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.02,0:14:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu, Jarashi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.03,0:14:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Agh. Dia benar-benar tak ada harapan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.67,0:14:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm... Aku harus bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.42,0:14:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yako.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.35,0:14:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.04,0:14:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah panggilkan taksi.\NAku akan mengantarmu pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.29,0:14:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.54,0:14:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-A-A-Apa yang harus kulakukan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.25,0:14:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apakah aku ajak dia minum teh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.13,0:14:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu, apa ruanganku cukup rapi\Nuntuk biarkan orang masuk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.84,0:14:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yako.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.62,0:14:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.38,0:14:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada restoran yang bikin aku penasaran.\NMau pergi bersamaku kapan-kapan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.60,0:14:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu restoran makan gelap.\NKita makan di ruangan gelap gulita.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.54,0:14:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}O-Oh! Aku pernah dengar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.57,0:15:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kupikir mungkin itu akan membuatku\Nbisa rasakan duniamu, entah bagaimana.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.85,0:15:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau mau?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.00,0:15:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Merasakan duniaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.66,0:15:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Izinkan aku mengawalmu, Tonome.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.72,0:15:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan mengandalkanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.28,0:15:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih sudah antarkan aku pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.36,0:15:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan sungkan.\NKalau begitu, sampai besok.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.63,0:15:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Anu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.63,0:15:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.58,0:15:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ma...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.59,0:15:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maukah kau masuk minum teh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.28,0:15:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.93,0:15:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Argo taksinya masih jalan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.87,0:15:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah. Benar juga...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.09,0:15:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi jika kau mau, lain kali aku akan\Nmenerima tawaranmu dengan senang hati.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.46,0:15:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat malam.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.68,0:15:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Se-Selamat... malam...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.85,0:15:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Aku perlu minta seseorang\Nperiksa ruanganku...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.86,0:15:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yako.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.15,0:15:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.86,0:16:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pakaianmu indah malam ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.02,0:16:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Apa menurutmu begitu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.38,0:16:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mengandalkanmu\Nuntuk mengawalku malam ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.82,0:16:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Aku akan lakukan yang terbaik!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.96,0:16:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tonome, bagaimana? Sangat gelap\Nsampai kau tak bisa melihat apa pun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.90,0:16:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, tidak, ada lilin kecil di atas meja.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.69,0:16:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang, Tuan dan Nyonya,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.50,0:16:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kami akan mematikan semua lampu\Ndan memberi kalian kegelapan sejati.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.37,0:16:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa sekarang gelap gulita?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.33,0:16:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, sudah gelap gulita.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.41,0:16:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tonome, selamat datang di duniaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.43,0:16:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apakah kau baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.58,0:16:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.79,0:16:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bisa mulai dengan rasakan apa\Ndan di mana benda di sekitarmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.75,0:16:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.40,0:16:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya Tonome sangat gugup.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.21,0:17:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini enak!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.38,0:17:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kau sudah coba terrine ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.19,0:17:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tonome?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.85,0:17:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Permisi, aku ke toilet dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.97,0:17:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.43,0:17:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.79,0:17:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yako?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.93,0:17:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, Tonome.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.63,0:17:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana kalau kita sudahi malam ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.82,0:17:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah... Begitu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.74,0:17:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.26,0:17:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sungguh minta maaf.\NAku yang mengajakmu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.70,0:17:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan khawatir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.50,0:17:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah merusak makan malam kita,\Ntapi aku akan menebusnya nanti.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.99,0:18:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan khawatir tentang itu juga!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.67,0:18:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku minta staf bungkus sisanya untuk kita!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.97,0:18:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah, bagus!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.68,0:18:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak sabar ingin memakannya di rumah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.90,0:18:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, aku juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.87,0:18:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau mau memakannya di rumahku?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.91,0:18:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh? Boleh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.69,0:18:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.34,0:18:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makan malam siap.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.75,0:18:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.82,0:18:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku letakkan semuanya di satu piring.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.81,0:18:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.32,0:18:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yakin mau sampanye?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.06,0:18:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.14,0:18:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gawat...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.49,0:18:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sangat gugup, sampai cuma bisa\Nberkata "Oh!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.76,0:18:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yako, aku minta maaf soal malam ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.38,0:18:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, tidak, tolong jangan dipikirkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.63,0:18:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya aku takut gelap.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.70,0:18:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Takut gelap?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.10,0:18:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa aku juga tahu penyebabnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.63,0:18:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tahu karyawisata semalam di SD?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.43,0:19:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebagai bagian perjalanan, ada uji nyali.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.21,0:19:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami harus bawa lilin\Ndan jalan di jalur pegunungan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.77,0:19:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah! Itu Kacchan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.66,0:19:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kacchan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.08,0:19:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.94,0:19:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.71,0:19:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Se-Seseorang...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.76,0:19:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku putuskan terlalu berbahaya\Nuntuk melanjutkan,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.92,0:19:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jadi aku menunggu bantuan di sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.48,0:19:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi tak ada yang datang.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku berhenti menunggu\Ndan berhasil jalan kembali ke penginapan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.69,0:19:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak ada yang sadar aku tak ada di sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.90,0:20:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak terlihat, jadi sama saja\Naku ada atau tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.29,0:20:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa trauma ini lebih besar\Ndari yang kukira.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.41,0:20:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mengalami kegelapan total di kota itu\Nsangat jarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.42,0:20:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak sadar begitu takut gelap.\NAku kaget sendiri hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.21,0:20:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus lebih berhati-hati\Nmulai sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.74,0:20:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tonome,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.70,0:20:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku akan menyadarinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.19,0:20:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yako...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.09,0:20:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suaramu bersih dan stabil.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.17,0:20:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sangat mudah untuk tahu\Nsaat kau merasa tak tenang.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.35,0:20:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, saat ini, kau berusaha\Nbersikap ceria dan tenang,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.03,0:20:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi suara gelasmu\Ndan kecepatan minummu tak stabil.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.84,0:20:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu kau sangat ketakutan dan sedih.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.87,0:20:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan merasa sangat kesepian\Njika kau tak ada, Tonome.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.88,0:20:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pasti akan pergi mencarimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.44,0:21:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apakah kau mau mulai berpacaran?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.70,0:21:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.58,0:21:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.02,0:21:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh? Reaksimu begitu saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.08,0:21:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ti-Tidak, bukannya aku menentangnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.35,0:21:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.88,0:21:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku merasa akan sangat bahagia\Njika kau ada di sisiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.30,0:21:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apakah kau merasakan hal yang sama, Yako?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.10,0:21:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Uh... Ah... Tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.88,0:21:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika kita mulai berkencan sekarang,\Napa yang terjadi setelah ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.22,0:21:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.06,0:21:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak! Tidak!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.31,0:21:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku berencana mengantarmu,\Nlalu langsung pulang hari ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.03,0:21:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Hari ini"?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.42,0:21:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, Yako, tapi ini meresahkan...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.99,0:21:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.39,0:21:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, kau ingin\Nsesuatu terjadi malam ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.30,0:21:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.32,0:21:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa itu?\NKedengarannya seperti efek suara.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.43,0:21:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu suara hatiku yang sama sekali tak siap!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.84,0:22:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, ya, aku sudah tahu itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.87,0:22:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.44,0:22:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mencintaimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.14,0:22:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kyaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.92,0:22:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Kyaa"?
